<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(28px, 8vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 16px;">About PostureTru</h1>
    <p style="font-size: clamp(15px, 3.5vw, 18px); color: var(--color-text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      A smarter approach to better posture.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Brand Story -->
<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container about-story">
    <h2>Where It Started</h2>
    <p>PostureTru began with a simple realization.</p>
    <p>After years of working long hours at a desk, I noticed the same pattern almost every day. I would start the morning sitting upright, focused and energized. A few hours later, without realizing it, I would be leaning forward with rounded shoulders and a stiff neck.</p>
    <p>The problem was never knowing what good posture looked like. The problem was remembering it while I was busy working.</p>
    <p>When I looked at existing posture products, most relied on discomfort or restriction. They reminded you by forcing your body into position, but they did not help build lasting habits.</p>
    <p>I wanted something different. Instead of correcting posture through force, I wanted a product that simply brought awareness back at the exact moment it mattered. A gentle reminder that lets your body do the rest.</p>
    <p>That idea became PostureTru.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission -->
<section class="section-padding" style="background-color: var(--color-bg-light); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="container about-story">
    <h2 id="mission">Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe better posture begins with awareness.</p>
    <p>As more people work from home and spend their days in front of screens, maintaining healthy posture has become harder than ever. It is not that people do not care. It is that they are focused on their work.</p>
    <p>Our mission is to create thoughtful products that fit naturally into modern life, helping people build healthier habits without adding friction to their day.</p>
    <p>Every decision we make is guided by three principles: design products people actually enjoy using, make premium wellness technology accessible, and build habits that last rather than temporary fixes.</p>
    <p>PostureTru is not about forcing perfect posture. It is about helping people become more aware of how they move, sit, and work, one small reminder at a time.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Founder -->
<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container about-founder">
    <h2>From the Founder</h2>
    <blockquote class="founder-quote">
      "I built PostureTru because I could not find a posture solution I actually wanted to wear. As someone who spends most of the day at a desk, I wanted something simple, comfortable, and effective enough to become part of my everyday routine. That is the standard we continue to build toward."
    </blockquote>
    <p class="founder-attribution">— Kartik Sachdeva, Founder</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why Choose Us -->
<section class="section-padding" style="background-color: var(--color-bg);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Why Choose PostureTru</h2>
      <p style="white-space: nowrap; font-size: clamp(12px, 3.2vw, 18px);">Awareness leads to change more naturally than correction.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <!-- Col 1 -->
      <div class="pillar-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: nowrap;">Built for Remote Work</h3>
        <p>We understand long hours at a desk because we live them too. PostureTru is designed for the realities of remote work, study sessions, and screen focused routines where posture naturally declines over time.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 2 -->
      <div class="pillar-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: nowrap;">Premium Quality Fair Price</h3>
        <p>By keeping production direct and intentional, we focus on quality without unnecessary markup. PostureTru uses soft food grade silicone, durable ABS components, and a precision motion sensor designed for consistent everyday use.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 3 -->
      <div class="pillar-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: nowrap;">Designed Around Awareness</h3>
        <p>At its core, PostureTru uses real time motion sensing to detect when your posture begins to change. Instead of forcing correction, it delivers a subtle reminder that brings your attention back to your body, so better posture becomes something you naturally return to throughout the day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

